<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4;
      margin: 2.5cm 2.5cm;
    }
    body {
      font-family: "DejaVu Sans", Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 10pt;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .header-line {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .brand { font-size: 9pt; color: #555; }
    .doc-ref { font-size: 9pt; color: #888; text-align: right; }
    h1 {
      font-size: 18pt;
      text-align: center;
      color: #1e3a5f;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    }
    .doc-subtitle {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 10pt;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    hr { border: none; border-top: 2px solid #1e3a5f; margin: 16px 0; }
    .parties {
      display: flex;
      gap: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .party-box {
      flex: 1;
      background: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .party-label {
      font-size: 8pt;
      color: #64748b;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .party-name { font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt; }
    .party-detail { font-size: 9pt; color: #444; }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 10pt;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #1e3a5f;
      border-left: 4px solid #1e3a5f;
      padding-left: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0 10px 0;
    }
    .amounts-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    .amounts-table td {
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
      font-size: 10pt;
    }
    .amounts-table .label-col { color: #555; }
    .amounts-table .amount-col {
      text-align: right;
      font-weight: 500;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .amounts-table .total-row td {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 12pt;
      background: #eef2f7;
      color: #1e3a5f;
      border-top: 2px solid #1e3a5f;
    }
    .due-date-box {
      background: #fff7ed;
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 10pt;
    }
    .due-date-box strong { color: #c2410c; }
    .badge-brouillon {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #6b7280;
      color: white;
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 9pt;
      margin-left: 8px;
    }
    .badge-envoye {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #2563eb;
      color: white;
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 9pt;
      margin-left: 8px;
    }
    .badge-acquitte {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #16a34a;
      color: white;
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 9pt;
      margin-left: 8px;
    }
    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 5px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
      font-size: 9.5pt;
    }
    .info-row .ilabel { color: #555; }
    .info-row .ivalue { font-weight: 500; }
    .legal-mention {
      font-size: 8pt;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="header-line">
    <div class="brand">
      <strong>LeComptoirImmo</strong><br>
      Gestion locative
    </div>
    <div class="doc-ref">
      Réf. {{ avis.id | string | truncate(8, end='') }}<br>
      Émis le {{ avis.created_at.strftime('%d/%m/%Y') }}
      {% if avis.status == 'brouillon' %}
        <span class="badge-brouillon">Brouillon</span>
      {% elif avis.status == 'envoye' %}
        <span class="badge-envoye">Envoyé</span>
      {% elif avis.status == 'acquitte' %}
        <span class="badge-acquitte">Acquitté</span>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <h1>Avis d'échéance</h1>
  <p class="doc-subtitle">{{ avis.period_label }}</p>
  <hr>

  <!-- Parties -->
  <div class="parties">
    <div class="party-box">
      <div class="party-label">Bailleur / Gestionnaire</div>
      {% if property %}
      <div class="party-name">{{ property.name }}</div>
      <div class="party-detail">{{ property.full_address }}</div>
      {% if property.owner_name %}
      <div class="party-detail" style="margin-top:4px;">Propriétaire : {{ property.owner_name }}</div>
      {% endif %}
      {% else %}
      <div class="party-name">—</div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    <div class="party-box">
      <div class="party-label">Locataire</div>
      <div class="party-name">{{ avis.tenant.full_name if avis.tenant else '—' }}</div>
      <div class="party-detail">
        Logement : {{ avis.unit.unit_ref if avis.unit else '—' }}
        {% if property %}
        <br>{{ property.full_address }}
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Date d'échéance -->
  <div class="due-date-box">
    Loyer à régler avant le : <strong>{{ avis.due_date.strftime('%d/%m/%Y') }}</strong>
    {% if avis.lease and avis.lease.payment_method %}
    &nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp;Mode de paiement :
      {% if avis.lease.payment_method == 'virement' %}Virement bancaire
      {% elif avis.lease.payment_method == 'cheque' %}Chèque
      {% elif avis.lease.payment_method == 'prelevement' %}Prélèvement automatique
      {% else %}Espèces{% endif %}
    {% endif %}
  </div>

  <!-- Détail montants -->
  <div class="section-title">Détail de l'appel de loyer</div>

  <table class="amounts-table">
    <tr>
      <td class="label-col">Loyer hors charges</td>
      <td class="amount-col">{{ "%.2f"|format(avis.amount_rent|float) }} €</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="label-col">Provisions sur charges</td>
      <td class="amount-col">{{ "%.2f"|format(avis.amount_charges|float) }} €</td>
    </tr>
    {% if avis.amount_apl %}
    <tr>
      <td class="label-col">Déduction APL (tiers-payant CAF)</td>
      <td class="amount-col">- {{ "%.2f"|format(avis.amount_apl|float) }} €</td>
    </tr>
    {% endif %}
    <tr class="total-row">
      <td>Montant total à payer</td>
      <td class="amount-col">{{ "%.2f"|format(avis.amount_total|float) }} €</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  {% if avis.notes %}
  <!-- Notes -->
  <div class="section-title">Informations complémentaires</div>
  <p style="font-size: 9.5pt; color: #444;">{{ avis.notes }}</p>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- Mention légale -->
  <div class="legal-mention">
    Cet avis d'échéance est établi conformément aux dispositions du bail en vigueur.
    Il ne constitue pas une quittance de loyer. La quittance vous sera remise après
    encaissement du paiement.
    Document généré automatiquement par LeComptoirImmo.
  </div>

</body>
</html>
